During stage 1 of the project Skiff Street traffic will be shifted to the south side of the bridge with one lane of traffic in each direction while the bridge is widened and replaced. Traffic will then be shifted to the north side of the bridge on the new structure while the south side is replaced. Construction activity may impact traffic on Route 15. Lane closures may occur between 7 PM and 10 PM but in all cases traffic must be restored by 6 AM on all weekday mornings.
